\
5. There is now a status bar that will give you the progress when a level is loading.\
\
6. The program will now alert you of many different problems that may come up (ie: It will tell you why if a poly can't be filled). Expect this to improve with future releases.\
\
7. The optimize button will set a flag for the window server that may improve drawing performance a little. Expect with a future release major speed improvements with scrolling and drawing!\
